Package: podlover
Type: Package
Title: Collects, Cleans and Analyzes Podcast Download Data from Podlove Publisher
Version: 1.0.4
Authors@R: person("Timm", "Suess", email = "catchall@sporez.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/lordyo/podlover
BugReports: https://github.com/lordyo/podlover/issues
Description: Connects to a specified Worpdress MySQL database running the
    Podlove Publisher plugin, collects all necessary tables for analysis of
    podcast download data, cleans the data for processing and provides various
    functions for descriptive, statistical and graphical analysis.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
