    ggplot2,
    ggrepel,
    keyring,
    lubridate,
    RMySQL,
    tidyr,
    rstudioapi,
    purrr,
    magrittr,
    ggridges,
    ggthemes,
    wakefield,
    tibble
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
